{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"1ad2ae0ae6","title":"中央首长接见西藏军区任荣等人时的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"45147cd843","index":0,"year":1967,"month":9,"day":18,"articleId":"1ad2ae0ae6","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"指示","id":"2d13338754","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"周恩来","id":"523bb79e8f","type":"人物"},{"name":"康生","id":"57eea82497","type":"人物"},{"name":"江青","id":"82305e518c","type":"人物"},{"name":"周总理","id":"838b5f2c9d","type":"人物"},{"name":"边境地区和少数民族","id":"c0cd6cf1d4","type":"主题"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"陈伯达","id":"e46e45351b","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"48606ca4e5","name":"陈伯达"},{"id":"8bb7755376","name":"康生"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"f2393e473f","type":"title","text":"中央首长接见西藏军区任荣等人时的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"1ad2ae0ae6","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"033e1b63c1","type":"paragraph","text":"〖九月十八日晚上八点二十四分到十一点三十分，周总理、伯达、康生、江青、富治、文元、法宪，接见了西藏军区任荣、陈明义、张鹤田和苗丕一、周仁山、任荣等同志向中央首长汇报了西藏文化大革命的问题后，中央对西藏问题作了如下指示。〗","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"1ad2ae0ae6","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"968ec646a6","type":"paragraph","text":"一、拉萨两派均定为革命群众组织，实行革命大批判、大联合；","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"1ad2ae0ae6","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"04472e03a5","type":"paragraph","text":"二、拉萨各派组织必须马上停止武斗，不准调农民，牧民进城。凡是已经调进城的，立即劝说他们回去；","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"1ad2ae0ae6","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"fc3b3c1c41","type":"paragraph","text":"三、抓革命、促生产、促战备、促工作，立即恢复交通运输，保证交通畅通；","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"1ad2ae0ae6","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"409a0ce0c9","type":"paragraph","text":"四、防止坏人挑拨离间，搞破坏，挑拨民族关系、军民关系，不要上敌人的当；","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"1ad2ae0ae6","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4df4404b69","type":"paragraph","text":"五、立即出《西藏日报》电讯版，报纸要传达毛主席、党中央的声音，这是天经地义的，《西藏日报》应立即出版，谁不这样做，就是对抗中央。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"1ad2ae0ae6","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"518dcc3cb7","type":"paragraph","text":"以上各点，看那一个革命组织执行得好，这是对革命组织的一个考验，谁按这个执行的就是站在毛主席的革命路线上，要求双方对以上问题达成协议。","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"1ad2ae0ae6","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1a6693cd97","type":"paragraph","text":"（根据任荣同志传达记录整理）","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"1ad2ae0ae6","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}